item.title: thanks
item.description: thanks for ordering! While waiting for our account manager to contact you, you can take a look at http://themes.gohugo.io/ to see what kind of layout you like. If you do not have photos available, free beautiful images are available at http://www.unsplash.com. Thats where we usually go to to get images for our customers. You should expect to get an email within the next working day.
